{"tid":705614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 偷麵包男哀號：「我冇嘢食，要返工。」","createTime":"2018-06-17T09:59:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T11:25:31.000Z","uid":19454,"like":22,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"d32c99c6a85d6efd57dfb99c0a991d9eaba976cc","tid":705614,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T09:59:26.000Z","msg":"港鐵彩虹站一間OK便利店內，涉嫌盜竊價值共40港元的一袋麵包和兩袋焗豆，被女職員揭破後，有人疑棄載有贓物的白色膠袋拔足逃走，女店員檢起尾隨追捕，在場東網記者拍下追捕過程。<br />\n<br />\n影片顯示，女店員沿途不停叫「你唔可以咁走嘅，咁樣唔得嘅」，同時高呼「偷嘢」，多名熱心市民聞訊，包括藝人黃建東，亦加入追捕行列。橙衫男越閘逃入車站大堂，但最終被見義勇為市民截獲，將其按在地下，女店員亦尾隨追至，不斷話他「唔可以走，你做乜偷嘢」，橙衫男則稱「<span style=\"color: red;\">我冇嘢食，要返工。」</span>期間，港鐵職員接報到場，有人則報警。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180617/bkn-20180617013225827-0617_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180617%2Fbkn-20180617013225827-0617_00822_001.html&d=aqXD9y8er%2F9LZiUwGWhVE%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=2399fc60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180617/bkn-20180617013225827-0617_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"56227ca10b04f54da460a760d506c849d0d40a73","tid":705614,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":71,"score":-69,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T09:59:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180617/photo/bkn-20180617013225827-0617_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180617173443\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180617%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180617013225827-0617_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180617173443&h=a7533739&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92ba8b6ed461135715edccf197e2d4424ccb524e","tid":705614,"uid":19454,"like":248,"dislike":1,"score":247,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T10:00:39.000Z","msg":"好慘<br />\n<br />\n餓到冇麵包食，仲掛住返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"194d559c29c3f186dc306eb18f8713dcdd3c65fc","tid":705614,"uid":19454,"like":70,"dislike":1,"score":69,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"201